CatDescriptText: "Whether therefore ye eat, or drink, or whatever ye do, do all things to God's glory", written decorative letters is mounted on display in front of banquet tables.
TitMainTitle: Man standing with arms outstretched at podium with cross, between two men and three women seated at banquet table, with decorative letters draped across curtains in background reading "Ella Mae Philips Grand Associate Matron"
